<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>500 - Server Error</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>Strenger Talk</h1>
      <nav>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <hr />

    <main>
      <h2>500 - Internal Server Error</h2>

      <section>
        <p>
          <strong>An unexpected error has occurred.</strong>
        </p>

        <p>Error Details: <code><%= error %></code></p>

        <p>
          <a href="/">Go back to home page</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3>What should you do?</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Go back to the <a href="/">home page</a></li>
          <li>Try a different page or action</li>
          <li><a href="/contact">Contact us</a> if the problem persists</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <p>
          <em
            >If you believe this is a mistake, please contact us with details of
            what you were doing.</em
          >
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <hr />

    <footer>
      <p>&copy; 2025 Strenger Talk | Express.js with MVC Pattern</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
